{
  "stem": "9963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he asked the other ones, is that the truth?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, yes, that's the truth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jawohl, hauptsturmfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when they said this, so he checked with his [INAUDIBLE] and told to his assistant or another officer, he says, go down and give them 25 lashes, and let them live.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we got 25 lashes, and they let us live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To make the story shorter, I-- that stopped for a few days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't went, but later I had to go, because people need to eat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People, you know, were waiting for the food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I start working again like this, and we did that till the evacuation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The evacuation of that camp-- we were over there 5,500 people in that camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 1943. 5,500 plus-- men, women, and children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We evacuated the camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said 50 people will stay in the camp to dismantle the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So all the prominent people stayed in the camp, all the [NON-ENGLISH] with the their kapos, with all the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were 48 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They needed two more people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They came to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They want me to stay in the camp with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They said, we'll have here very good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We'll have enough to eat here, only 50 people of us, so it will be much easier-- and blah, blah, blah-- to stay with them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So-- and I was always that person to see what for more people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I told them, you know what, Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Krakauer, you can be here without me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You have to take somebody else because, you see, all the people here are stepped out, and I see all the people lined up, men, women, and children.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
